  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The journey from-- from-- to Vladivostok?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the journey as such, apart from the three days in Moscow and the experiences there, which may be of interest in terms of the observing life in Russia prior to the war, and seeing certain moments of people standing in a queue waiting for bread before the war started.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was in Moscow, not in the hinterland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- but-- but what I would maybe try to put to you is this-- the trip to Moscow-- from-- the trip from Vilna to Moscow, and then when we finally set off on the long journey of up via the Urals right all the way to Vladivostok, it was maybe-- it was not eventful, in terms of-- because you were in a small space, in a coupe with four people.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to sleep in that coupe and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in terms of emotions, it was very eventful [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can only judge myself by my own emotions, because you had a-- a composite of-- of realizations, and awarenesses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the one hand, you were aware that you are escaping Europe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You are Leaving Europe behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And especially, you are getting-- you are just about to finalize the last act of outwitting Stalin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have outwitted Hitler already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have, personally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I am in the last act of outwitting Stalin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- that sort of inner realization of an awareness that, somehow, miraculous as that may sound-- and it was, and it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To get a transit visa from-- and to get all this, too, and to be actually physically on that train, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
